            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Fritz! I brought the material you requested!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ah, thanks for that. With this, I should be able to create a magnificent doll."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Ehehe, that's good!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Sophie, thank you again. This brings me one step closer to my dream."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "To put on the greatest puppet show... Right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. Once this doll is complete, I plan to use it in my grand puppet show."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Wow, that's great!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "But is it really okay for me to have made a material for something so amazing...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "What are you talking about? That's exactly why I asked you to make it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Not only are you a brilliant alchemist, but you also have a love for dolls. That's why I left it to you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Fritz...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "You really are a capable alchemist. Far greater than you seem to think. You should have more confidence in yourself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Thank you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, I want to start work on my doll using this material now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "You'll be the first person I show when it's complete. Look forward to it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Yes, I'll be waiting!"
        }
    ]
}